msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <dl><dl><dd><p>
#: complete.html:878
msgid ""
"Long answer: probably, but only to someone working on the package you're "
"trying to compile. Mostly, everything will be fine unless make quits with an "
"error."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <dl><dl><dd><p>
#: complete.html:881
